{"id": "1211983372679647334", "channel_id": "1211983372679647334", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "地圖我全部走一圈了。\n進去Boss前，剩餘13黑印\n\n結算後，分數一樣是只有13黑印。\n\n這張命輪，在深潛是否不會增加黑印？", "timestamp": "2024-02-27T10:29:13.609000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1211983373090684928", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-27-18-25-47-301_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 118832, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1211983372679647334/1211983373090684928/Screenshot_2024-02-27-18-25-47-301_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg?ex=6a005df9&is=69ff0c79&hm=96a0dcb01b6f0c87baae71300912b44ff13697920eabdc535ff5d4e1504df40d&"}, {"id": "1211983373451403334", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-27-18-24-32-204_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 175577, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1211983372679647334/1211983373451403334/Screenshot_2024-02-27-18-24-32-204_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg?ex=6a005df9&is=69ff0c79&hm=19f583c3c2ae3db5f94dca8acfb7c0e9e8e383d2bebb0579d1db6b19b5c542d5&"}, {"id": "1211983373715775509", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-27-18-24-14-577_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 115234, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1211983372679647334/1211983373715775509/Screenshot_2024-02-27-18-24-14-577_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg?ex=6a005df9&is=69ff0c79&hm=0cfdc658e31979e2bd2cca1c2aa28549badcf8171c3f61bd4910e6e4ff4df1c3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1211983372679647334", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」命輪：洞悉。深潛地圖全開不會+20黑印？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1211908299239333908", "channel_id": "1211908299239333908", "type": 0, "author_id": "1187994440019746886", "author_name": "kkklavier", "author_bot": false, "content": "既然都已經開放助戰模式，感覺應該可以有更多花樣（像是每回合選取友方隊伍三張卡牌之類的）\n我的意思不是要再增加一個幕間演習，而是覺得應該有更多特殊玩法的期間限定活動\n在等待主線又沒有潛遊可以打的時候，並不是每個人都喜歡打什麼困難超困難爆炸困難\n希望能給休閒玩家一些輕鬆的限定活動～\n我是真的很喜歡這個遊戲（尤其是畫風）所以也很希望它的壽命可以長一點😅😅", "timestamp": "2024-02-27T05:30:54.706000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1211908299239333908", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」何時能有特別活動企劃", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
